WEBVTT

00:02.800 --> 00:04.800
把这个地方想像成美国地图
Think of this place like a map of the US.

00:04.810 --> 00:07.340
我们的牢房那边  那是纽约城
Our cell over there, that's New York City.

00:07.350 --> 00:09.950
医务室 我们的出口  是加利福尼亚
The infirmary, our exit, that's California.

00:09.960 --> 00:12.530
我们脚下连接两边的管道...
The pipes beneath us that connect the two...

00:12.540 --> 00:14.380
-66号公路  -我们要离开的必经之路
-Route 66.  -Our ticket out of here.

00:14.390 --> 00:16.850
66公路直接在那个房子下面经过
Route 66 runs beneath that building.

00:16.860 --> 00:19.640
那是管道上方的唯一建筑
It's the only building sitting on top of those tunnels.

00:19.650 --> 00:22.770
我们要做的就是以P.I.的身份进里面去
All we gotta do is get in there,on PI,

00:22.780 --> 00:25.280
给我们自己挖个出口
and dig ourselves an onramp.

00:25.650 --> 00:27.740
-在哪?  -就这
-Which one?  -Right there.

00:27.850 --> 00:30.710
这里4英尺下面连接主管道
This goes down four feet.Connects to the main line below.

00:30.720 --> 00:32.230
我们要做的就是加宽它
All we've gotta do is widen it

00:32.240 --> 00:35.180
这样66号公路就有了出口
and we've got ourselves an onramp to Route 66.

00:35.190 --> 00:36.480
我要弄清楚
I'm gonna find out, you know,

00:36.490 --> 00:38.020
你在上面干什么
what it is you're doing up there.

00:38.030 --> 00:39.620
你说你到天花板上去
You told me that you had been up

00:39.630 --> 00:43.380
是为了P.I.的工作 但...
in the crawlspace for PI,

00:43.390 --> 00:45.460
P.I.从来没有派过这样的任务
and PI was never assigned to go there.

00:45.470 --> 00:46.680
我们给你...
We got you...

00:46.690 --> 00:48.880
一个小礼物
a little get well gift.

00:48.890 --> 00:51.340
你叫什么?
What's your name?

00:51.700 --> 00:53.930
发生了一起爆炸事故
There was an explosion.

00:53.940 --> 00:55.910
煤气管道爆炸  里面所有人都死了
Gas line. Everyone inside was killed.

00:55.920 --> 00:58.000
我们对抗的这伙人  不把我们干掉不会罢休的
These people won't stop until we're dead.

00:58.010 --> 00:59.230
我们不能永远躲下去
We can't hide forever.

00:59.240 --> 01:01.720
那个孩子呢  据说杀了父母的那个?
How about that kid?The one killed his parents?

01:01.730 --> 01:03.310
-哦  他被抓了  -真的?
Oh, they got him. -They did?

01:03.320 --> 01:04.180
他已经在看管之下
He's in custody.

01:04.190 --> 01:06.290
我知道你的样子  你这狗杂种!
I know what you look like, you son of a bitch.

01:06.300 --> 01:07.750
菲利·法尔曾
Philly Falzone.

01:07.760 --> 01:10.490
你知道这里有人知道他的下落
Word is someone knows where Fibonacci is

01:10.500 --> 01:13.180
无论如何也要想办法
and you're not doing anything about it.

01:20.060 --> 01:22.460
帮帮我
Help me.

01:23.870 --> 01:25.670
求你了
Please.

01:35.100 --> 01:38.160
你要原谅这个孩子
You'll have to forgive my boy.

01:38.170 --> 01:44.160
他老是做些不应该做的事
He has the propensity to be a bit gregarious when he shouldn't be.

01:44.170 --> 01:46.870
在监狱的浴室总是感到很害怕
Fraternising in the prison shower. Come on.

01:46.870 --> 01:49.990
也许你该让他歇一会
Maybe you oughta cut the kid a break.

01:50.000 --> 01:55.520
你是不是对我的行为有意见啊  你没这么蠢吧
You wouldn't be meddling in my affairs,now, would you?You can't be that stupid.

01:55.800 --> 01:59.330
现在我跟你算是同一条船上的人了
Not while I'm so fully invested in your affairs.

02:04.080 --> 02:08.600
这是你们两个之间的事  与我无关
What's between you and him is between you and him.

02:09.000 --> 02:11.800
我就这个意思
That's what I thought you said.

02:23.070 --> 02:26.950
你一定要帮我
You've gotta help me.

02:32.850 --> 02:34.810
你一定要帮我
You gotta help me.

02:34.820 --> 02:37.140
你找错人了  这是警察的事
You talk to the wrong man.This is a matter for the police.

02:37.150 --> 02:38.580
我说的可是我儿子
This is my son we're talking about.

02:38.590 --> 02:41.080
看在上帝的份上  他失踪了  帮帮我!
For god say,He's missing. Do something!

02:41.090 --> 02:44.760
你必须明白 我只是个监狱的狱长
You have got to understand,I am the warden of a prison.

02:44.770 --> 02:46.130
牵涉到法律问题
When it comes to the law,

02:46.140 --> 02:48.150
我完全无能为力
absolutely there is nothing I can do.

02:48.160 --> 02:50.940
外面发生的事完全超出我的权力范围
Whatever happens is out of my jurisdiction

02:50.950 --> 02:52.340
除非事情在里面
until it comes through those gates.

02:52.350 --> 02:55.090
这就是里面的事!  放我出去!
It just did. Let me out.

02:55.100 --> 02:56.950
-什么?  -让我去找他
-What?  -Let me find him.

02:56.960 --> 02:59.380
我了解他的想法  我知道他会去哪
I know how he thinks.I know where he'd run.

02:59.390 --> 03:00.660
布伦斯  现在跟你说清楚
I'd have thought

03:00.670 --> 03:04.890
以目前的情况  你应该清楚自己是个死囚
by now you'd understand your position as a death row inmate.

03:04.900 --> 03:07.510
这个忙我绝对帮不了
There is no way I can honour that request.

03:07.520 --> 03:10.060
你说谎.你有这权力
That ain't true.You get the power.

03:10.070 --> 03:13.200
如果犯人家属有紧急情况  你可以批准假释
In case of a family emergency,you can grant an inmate supervised leave.

03:13.210 --> 03:18.040
你儿子现在是杀人案的首要嫌疑人!
Your son is a prime suspect in a double homicide.

03:35.120 --> 03:38.780
你以为来干什么的  午休?
What do you think this is, a siesta?

03:38.790 --> 03:43.800
看到没有?看到我的脸在上面没有?  知道这是什么意思吗?
You see that? You see my face up there?Any idea how it got there?

03:43.810 --> 03:45.840
工作积极性
Work ethic.

03:45.850 --> 03:48.920
这个词在你们国家有什么意义吗?
Those two words mean anything in your country?

03:48.930 --> 03:51.380
你是狱工  在这里可不允许偷懒
You're on PI, so quit slow-walking me.

03:51.390 --> 03:52.940
下次就不只是警告了
I'm not gonna warn you again.

03:52.950 --> 03:56.620
看什么?!
What are you looking at?

04:26.420 --> 04:29.540
狱警发现碎块  就会知道我们在挖洞
The bulls find this stuff,they'll know we're digging.

04:29.550 --> 04:32.330
