I'm fitting to bounce.

10:16.000 --> 10:19.020
别激动
Peace.

10:22.970 --> 10:27.000
那个小子没意识到自己的肤色啊
Boy's a bit confused about his pigmentation,

10:27.010 --> 10:30.820
但他还是有勇气的  是吧
but he sure does have spunk, doesn't he?

