阿布鲁奇?
Abruzzi!

10:38.730 --> 10:42.980
-是?  -在干什么?
-Yeah?  -What are you doing?

10:43.760 --> 10:46.630
你说"在干什么?" 是什么意思?
What do you mean, what am I doing?

10:46.640 --> 10:49.760
月初就要到了  约翰
First of the month's coming up, John.

