11:11.780 --> 11:14.430
今天结束前我会回办公室
I'm going back into my office at the end of the day.

11:14.440 --> 11:16.530
再查我的收支情况
Gonna check my balance again.

11:16.540 --> 11:19.240
如果没解决的话...
If it's not up to where it's supposed to be,

11:19.250 --> 11:23.530
对你所有的照顾  比如负责P.I.
all these privileges you got,like running PI,

11:23.540 --> 11:27.160
都会消失
they're gone.

11:27.170 --> 11:30.240
搞定它  约翰
Get it done, John.

