He only wore it when he really,

12:36.970 --> 12:40.880
重要时才戴
really meant business.

12:41.530 --> 12:43.950
我们再露面会很危险
Be dangerous showing our faces again.

12:43.960 --> 12:47.250
除非他们不再找我们  他们认为我们已经死了  是吧?
Not if they're not looking for us.They think we're dead.

12:47.260 --> 12:49.930
