Come on, baby, say it.

14:54.190 --> 14:57.400
你就是狱长  路易斯!
You're the warden, Louis!

15:13.200 --> 15:16.740
这对婊子养的
The sneaky son of a bitch.

15:16.750 --> 15:20.020
